Leroy Jethro Gibbs is a fictional character of the CBS TV series NCIS , portrayed by Mark Harmon .
He is a former U.S Marine Corps Scout Sniper turned special agent who commands a team for the Naval Criminal Investigative Service .
Gibbs is the most accomplished marksman on the team and the most skilled at handling violent standoffs ; he depends on his other agents heavily for technical forensics and background checks .
He is patient but firm with his team and has little patience for bureaucracy ; he commands most other main characters -- including his current staff Timothy McGee , Ellie Bishop , Nick Torres and Alexandra Quinn and previous staff Caitlin Todd -LRB- killed in the line of duty -RRB- , Anthony DiNozzo -LRB- left to look after his newly found daughter -RRB- , and Ziva David -LRB- killed after leaving NCIS -RRB-